reviewText: Maybe you always wanted to see the inside of an upscale strip club. Well, here's you chance! Four hours of eye candy as there are 50 girls who show off their wares. That's nearly five minutes per performer. Watch it at home and save the cost of parking, cover charge, getting soused with overpriced drinks. You'll never run out of singles for tips, either. At any rate, the DVD is a great bargain.
